Individual




A. Clayton Perfall



Mr. A. C. Perfall is Managing Member at Union Street Capital Management LLC, a Member at World Presidents' Organization and a Member at Young Presidents' Organization, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Colfax Corp., Comstock Holding Cos., Inc., Affinity Direct LLC, Archway Holdings Corp., Distinct Holdings Group LLC, RT Acquisition Corp., Tailwind Premier Holdings LLC and Mason School of Business Foundation. Mr. Perfall was previously employed as an Advisor by Convergent Wealth Advisors LLC, Chief Executive Officer by Union Street Acquisition Corp., Chief Executive Officer & Director by AHL Services, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Convergence Holdings Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Director by Snyder Communications, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Archway Marketing Services, Inc., and Partner-Tax Advisory Services Group by Arthur Andersen LLP. He also served on the board at inVentiv Health, Inc., Imagitas, Inc. and Ventiv Health, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The College of William & Mary.



