Insider Activity


Individual




A. Clayton Perfall



Mr. A. C. Perfall is Independent Director at Colfax Corp., Independent Director at Comstock Holding Cos., Inc., Managing Member at Union Street Capital Management LLC, a Member at Young Presidents' Organization, Inc., and a Member at World Presidents' Organization. He is on the Board of Directors at Colfax Corp., Comstock Holding Cos., Inc., Affinity Direct LLC, Archway Holdings Corp., Mason School of Business Foundation, and RT Acquisition Corp.
Mr. Perfall was previously employed as an Advisor by Convergent Wealth Advisors LLC, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Archway Marketing Services, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Union Street Acquisition Corp., Chief Executive Officer & Director by AHL Services, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Convergence Holdings Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Director by Snyder Communications, Inc., and Partner-Tax Advisory Services Group by Arthur Andersen LLP. He also served on the board at inVentiv Health, Inc. and Imagitas, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The College of William & Mary.



